data.description: PRICE REDUCTION once more! Brand New roof November 2023  Welcome to your spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in coastal Port Charlotte with a screened in lanai and a good size in ground pool. The yard is landscaped beautifully and fenced for your pets. This home is situated just 30 minutes away from several great beaches. This could be a great investment property or your new dream home. Uniquely private, yet minutes to local restaurants, Port Charlotte Town Center Mall, and Port Charlotte Beach Park, with a public boat launch and fishing pier. Picture as you enter the high ceilings, open concept, and well-equipped kitchen with Granite countertops and ceramic tile throughout. The spacious inviting master bedroom is separated from the two guest bedrooms.  The pool is complete, no waiting to put one in. The screened in lanai, and the pool area has two covered areas.  It is a great spot for entertaining or invites relaxation and leisure. NO HOA fees! Such a great location to shopping and many restaurants, literally 4miles away. Twenty minutes to the Punta Gorda Airport. Fifteen minutes to the new Sunseeker Resort, with upscale restaurants and spa, now opened and a great spot to visit.  The popular Fishermans Village gives boat tours, has shops, and restaurants. A great spot to bring your company and visit. A weekend farmers market is close by, every Saturday.  Are you ready for lots of sunshine and living the Florida dream? So many things to do close by. A really great area to live. 15 minutes to I-75 with easy access to other Florida cities.  Hurry come get your piece of paradise, in this lovely 3 bed 2 bath home.  Don't miss out.
